<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ḥbdẖạ rạʿ ʿẓym</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ḥabãdẖā rāʿiⁿ ʿaẓīm̊ .. ḥāfiẓuⁿ ại̹lay̱ ạltãmām̊
 fī yadaẙhi kulũnā .. fī ạảmāniⁿ wasalạm̊

[V2]
 2- wāi̹lay̱ ạl̊maj̊di ạlsãnī̃̊ .. sayaqūdu jam̊ʿanā
 lạisẖ̊tirākiⁿ maʿahu .. fī ạlsũrūri wāl̊hanā

[V3]
 3- fal̊takun̊ ạảḥ̊qāwủnā .. dāyỉmaⁿạ muman̊ṭaqah̊
 wakadẖā qulūbunā .. biạlrãjāʾi wātẖiqah̊</lyrics>
</song>